window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I am completely and obsessively in love with my best friend's sister.</p> <p>Twenty years ago I was saved by the Volkov brothers and I made a vow… to protect their younger sister, Lara, with my life.</p> <p>And not a day goes by that I don’t take that seriously.</p> <p>She is my best friend and the keeper of my sanity.</p> <p>And when our enemies try to take her from me, they will pay the price with their life.</p> <p>I told her one kiss wouldn’t ruin our friendship.</p> <p>I was so very wrong.</p> <p>She is sweeter than any addiction.</p> <p>I may be crazy, but that is nothing in comparison to the way I feel about my pchelka.</p> <p>So I take matters into my own hands; I will never go back on my promise.</p> <p>Even if that means watching her as she sleeps.</p> <p>Except, what I didn’t realize, is this was never about protection, I did all of this out of love.</p> <p>With her, I stand to lose everything.</p> <p>Without her, I lose my mind… and my heart. Even when we’re torn apart, there isn’t a single force on this earth that can stop me from protecting her.</p> <p>Not even her brothers.</p> <p>I can save her from any dangers in the outside world, but will my love be enough to save her from the demons in her mind?</p>"; 
